WEBVTT

1
00:00:07.333 --> 00:00:09.333
[enthralling music playing]

2
00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:17.074
Support us and become VIP member 
to remove all ads from www.OpenSubtitles.org

3
00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:20.166
[engine revving]

4
00:00:31.666 --> 00:00:33.958
-[tires screeching]
-[engine revving]

5
00:00:46.541 --> 00:00:48.791
-[engine stops]
-[lighter clinks]

6
00:00:48.875 --> 00:00:50.416
-[inhaling]
-[crackling]

7
00:00:53.250 --> 00:00:55.000
[exhales]

8
00:00:56.833 --> 00:00:57.833
[chuckles]

9
00:00:58.625 --> 00:01:00.125
[groans]

10
00:01:10.666 --> 00:01:12.000
Hey. are you with him?

11
00:01:12.708 --> 00:01:13.791
Good. Come on then.

12
00:01:15.041 --> 00:01:15.875
Come on.

13
00:01:24.875 --> 00:01:26.958
-Oh. shit! [panting]
-[grunts]

14
00:01:34.000 --> 00:01:36.041
[both grunting]

15
00:01:41.041 --> 00:01:42.708
[straining]

16
00:01:53.916 --> 00:01:55.458
-[groans]
-[both grunting]

17
00:01:59.875 --> 00:02:00.708
[yelps]

18
00:02:03.541 --> 00:02:04.916
[weights clanking]

19
00:02:23.250 --> 00:02:24.375
[clanking]

20
00:02:25.416 --> 00:02:27.166
[growls. yells]

21
00:02:31.583 --> 00:02:33.250
[groaning]

22
00:02:36.208 --> 00:02:37.791
[yells. grunts]

23
00:02:40.000 --> 00:02:40.958
[gasps]

24
00:02:47.833 --> 00:02:49.541
[creaking]

25
00:02:57.125 --> 00:02:59.125
[thunder rumbling]

26
00:03:04.833 --> 00:03:06.833
[objects clattering]

27
00:03:10.250 --> 00:03:12.750
[breath trembling] I give up.

28
00:03:12.833 --> 00:03:13.916
[tuts]

29
00:03:15.625 --> 00:03:18.125
[whimpering]

30
00:03:19.125 --> 00:03:22.000
Deadbeats like you never learn
till someone beats it in to you.

31
00:03:23.958 --> 00:03:26.791
[whimpering] I give up.
Please let me go. just this once.

32
00:03:27.750 --> 00:03:30.458
I'll get the money
and pay you back as soon as I can.

33
00:03:31.083 --> 00:03:33.291
-Just this once. please--
-[thuds]

34
00:03:35.625 --> 00:03:36.458
[gasps]

35
00:03:37.125 --> 00:03:40.125
You don't pay again. I'll gut you
and feed you to the dogs.

36
00:03:51.166 --> 00:03:52.208
[wheezes]

37
00:03:53.916 --> 00:03:55.916
[thunder rumbling]

38
00:03:59.958 --> 00:04:02.250
[woman screaming]

39
00:04:02.333 --> 00:04:09.333
THE DEBT COLLECTOR

40
00:04:11.541 --> 00:04:16.375
{\an8}HIGH VOLTAGE
DANGEROUS

41
00:04:16.458 --> 00:04:20.500
{\an8}ZONE 3
AUTHORIZED ENTRY ONLY

42
00:04:20.583 --> 00:04:22.791
{\an8}[abbot] <i>Inadanam dukkham loke.</i>

43
00:04:24.000 --> 00:04:26.541
Debt causes suffering in this world.

44
00:04:26.625 --> 00:04:27.791
10 YEARS LATER

45
00:04:27.875 --> 00:04:31.375
And in the Dhamma.
it is the debt of karma.

46
00:04:32.416 --> 00:04:38.208
Good and evil are the cause
of happiness and suffering.

47
00:04:39.791 --> 00:04:41.708
The reason you are all here.

48
00:04:42.500 --> 00:04:45.708
is to repay the karmic debts
of your own making.

49
00:04:46.375 --> 00:04:47.708
You are confined.

50
00:04:48.666 --> 00:04:50.541
and subject to correction.

51
00:04:51.916 --> 00:04:54.625
While you are here.
you will come to your senses

52
00:04:56.125 --> 00:04:59.708
and learn the consequences
of your actions in time.

53
00:05:01.291 --> 00:05:03.541
You are nearing the end of your sentences.

54
00:05:04.291 --> 00:05:07.041
You have repaid your karmic debts.

55
00:05:08.041 --> 00:05:09.791
You are to begin a new life.

56
00:05:10.708 --> 00:05:13.500
Embrace integrity. Act with decorum.

57
00:05:14.375 --> 00:05:17.250
And be good members
of society from now on.

58
00:05:17.333 --> 00:05:18.958
May you all be blessed.

59
00:05:19.041 --> 00:05:21.333
[prisoners] <i>Sadhu.</i>

60
00:05:30.750 --> 00:05:32.583
[door opens]

61
00:05:39.666 --> 00:05:41.208
[door closes]

62
00:05:43.583 --> 00:05:48.416
PROVINCIAL PRISON

63
00:05:58.375 --> 00:06:00.375
[foreboding music playing]

64
00:06:08.291 --> 00:06:10.291
[hurried footsteps]

65
00:06:13.291 --> 00:06:14.125
[music stops]

66
00:06:19.833 --> 00:06:21.041
[retches. coughs]

67
00:06:29.958 --> 00:06:31.291
[Num] Where can I find the abbot?

68
00:06:31.375 --> 00:06:33.000
He's in the cave up on that mountain.

69
00:07:14.625 --> 00:07:16.750
Oh. it's you. Num.

70
00:07:18.750 --> 00:07:20.000
How did you get here?

71
00:07:21.791 --> 00:07:23.375
Have you already eaten?

72
00:07:26.125 --> 00:07:28.166
-I walked here. Father.
-Hmm.

73
00:07:28.958 --> 00:07:32.375
I wanted to pay my respects.

74
00:07:33.458 --> 00:07:34.375
Mm.

75
00:07:35.458 --> 00:07:37.541
You are released from your suffering.

76
00:07:39.166 --> 00:07:42.208
And from now on. you can begin anew.

77
00:07:44.875 --> 00:07:47.083
Have you thought about
how you'll make a living?

78
00:07:50.750 --> 00:07:51.583
Not yet.

79
00:07:57.416 --> 00:07:59.291
Uh. are you able to drive?

80
00:08:03.083 --> 00:08:05.541
-I am. yeah.
-Mm. that's good.

81
00:08:06.333 --> 00:08:09.750
One of my disciples
is looking for someone to do deliveries.

82
00:08:11.916 --> 00:08:12.958
Would you like that?

83
00:08:14.833 --> 00:08:16.541
I can put in a good word for you.

84
00:08:46.875 --> 00:08:49.416
[breathes deeply]

85
00:08:55.375 --> 00:08:56.333
[sighs softly]

86
00:08:59.875 --> 00:09:00.916
[sighs]

87
00:09:35.000 --> 00:09:36.791
[children chatter in distance]

88
00:10:01.000 --> 00:10:02.041
Delivery. sir.

89
00:10:09.541 --> 00:10:10.375
Delivery's here.

90
00:10:10.875 --> 00:10:13.083
{\an8}PETCH PRASERT

91
00:10:22.000 --> 00:10:24.916
BAD DRIVER:
BRING YOUR OWN GOOD KARMA

92
00:10:34.833 --> 00:10:38.166
JAI PETCH EXPRESS

93
00:10:46.625 --> 00:10:48.000
It's cute. actually.

94
00:10:49.333 --> 00:10:52.958
Wouldn't it be nice to keep
this cat with you as a companion?

95
00:10:53.791 --> 00:10:55.083
It wouldn't fare well.

96
00:10:57.500 --> 00:10:59.041
Can you please take care of it?

97
00:11:02.541 --> 00:11:03.375
Mm.

98
00:11:11.750 --> 00:11:13.750
[indistinct chatter]

99
00:11:18.625 --> 00:11:21.375
Ah. here it is. I hope you like that.

100
00:11:25.750 --> 00:11:26.791
What would you like?

101
00:11:27.875 --> 00:11:28.750
Uh…

102
00:11:29.750 --> 00:11:30.958
Bamboo shoots and a fried egg.

103
00:11:31.041 --> 00:11:32.250
-Over rice. right?
-Yeah.

104
00:12:16.416 --> 00:12:17.250
Mister.

105
00:12:18.916 --> 00:12:20.208
You forgot your money.

106
00:12:23.083 --> 00:12:24.208
Take it.

107
00:12:26.375 --> 00:12:27.791
You say thanks. Nid Noi.

108
00:12:28.958 --> 00:12:29.875
Thank you.

109
00:12:31.666 --> 00:12:32.500
Grandma.

110
00:12:33.166 --> 00:12:34.291
You hold on to it.

111
00:12:35.708 --> 00:12:38.000
[motorcycle engine revs aggressively]

112
00:12:54.666 --> 00:12:57.041
Okay. well. where is it? Huh?

113
00:13:09.291 --> 00:13:10.125
What's this?

114
00:13:11.833 --> 00:13:13.750
Take this for now. It's all I have.

115
00:13:14.291 --> 00:13:16.458
-Are you shitting me. huh?
-[gasps. whimpers]

116
00:13:17.041 --> 00:13:18.250
What the fuck?

117
00:13:19.041 --> 00:13:20.541
-[grunts]
-[people clamor]

118
00:13:21.750 --> 00:13:22.833
Screw you!

119
00:13:22.916 --> 00:13:23.958
Stop it! Stop!

120
00:13:26.916 --> 00:13:28.250
[whimpering]

121
00:13:29.458 --> 00:13:31.875
Don't. sir. You're scaring her.

122
00:13:32.583 --> 00:13:33.750
The girl's scared?

123
00:13:34.875 --> 00:13:37.541
-The girl's scared. is she?
-[Grandma Lek and Nid Noi yelp]

124
00:13:37.625 --> 00:13:38.458
Hey!

125
00:13:39.708 --> 00:13:40.916
Why should you care?

126
00:13:49.416 --> 00:13:51.375
Hey. motherfucker. Who are you?

127
00:13:52.666 --> 00:13:53.916
What do you want. huh?

128
00:13:57.791 --> 00:13:58.875
Look. please…

129
00:13:59.833 --> 00:14:00.916
leave.

130
00:14:01.000 --> 00:14:01.875
I'll pay.

131
00:14:03.458 --> 00:14:04.958
Just tell me what she owes you here.

132
00:14:06.000 --> 00:14:07.125
Give me 10.000.

133
00:14:10.375 --> 00:14:11.291
Give it to me!

134
00:14:24.500 --> 00:14:26.875
This is all I have. Just take it.

135
00:14:27.541 --> 00:14:28.375
Huh.

136
00:14:31.958 --> 00:14:33.541
-All right.
-[engines start]

137
00:14:35.125 --> 00:14:37.000
[revving]

138
00:14:38.750 --> 00:14:39.583
Ride.

139
00:14:48.833 --> 00:14:50.833
[indistinct chatter]

140
00:15:04.625 --> 00:15:05.458
Hey.

141
00:15:18.458 --> 00:15:19.875
-Hey.
-[hesitates]

142
00:15:22.083 --> 00:15:22.916
Here.

143
00:15:26.791 --> 00:15:27.625
That's all?

144
00:15:30.000 --> 00:15:31.708
Business has been bad. brother.

145
00:15:38.083 --> 00:15:39.625
-[grunts]
-Hey.

146
00:15:41.333 --> 00:15:42.916
I don't just want the interest.

147
00:15:44.375 --> 00:15:45.458
Okay?

148
00:15:46.250 --> 00:15:47.916
You got to pay the principal too.

149
00:15:48.458 --> 00:15:49.291
Understand?

150
00:15:49.875 --> 00:15:50.791
From now on.

151
00:15:51.750 --> 00:15:53.916
it's double the interest you'll pay me.

152
00:15:54.000 --> 00:15:55.083
Yes. Yes. sir.

153
00:15:56.916 --> 00:15:58.166
It's easy. really.

154
00:15:59.250 --> 00:16:00.250
[groans softly]

155
00:16:23.625 --> 00:16:25.625
[engine whirring]

156
00:16:33.000 --> 00:16:34.166
Turn left up ahead.

157
00:16:59.333 --> 00:17:00.333
[Grandma Lek] Thank you.

158
00:17:02.000 --> 00:17:03.625
Come inside. have some water.

159
00:17:07.500 --> 00:17:08.666
Sure.

160
00:17:08.750 --> 00:17:09.583
Good.

161
00:17:13.625 --> 00:17:15.125
Get him a water. okay?

162
00:17:33.875 --> 00:17:35.208
Just the two of you here?

163
00:17:36.958 --> 00:17:39.583
Yeah. Just me and my granddaughter.

164
00:17:39.666 --> 00:17:40.666
NID NOI LOVES GRANDMA

165
00:17:40.750 --> 00:17:42.416
Her mother left her with me.

166
00:17:44.666 --> 00:17:45.875
Then she disappeared.

167
00:17:48.500 --> 00:17:50.291
She hasn't sent a single baht.

168
00:17:52.583 --> 00:17:56.250
And the old age pension's
not enough to raise a child.

169
00:17:58.541 --> 00:18:02.291
So I've had to scrimp.
and… and run the stall.

170
00:18:06.750 --> 00:18:10.208
I didn't have anything
at the start. so I borrowed.

171
00:18:14.375 --> 00:18:15.458
How much do you owe?

172
00:18:17.833 --> 00:18:20.458
[sighs] 30.000.

173
00:18:22.500 --> 00:18:27.083
I used it to buy the cart
and to get other supplies.

174
00:18:31.166 --> 00:18:32.666
The interest is 1.000.

175
00:18:35.250 --> 00:18:37.625
Per day. So. before I knew it…

176
00:18:38.458 --> 00:18:39.458
[crying]

177
00:18:42.833 --> 00:18:45.583
…I owed over 100.000. [sniffling]

178
00:18:49.833 --> 00:18:52.166
Where will I ever get that sort of cash?

179
00:19:13.500 --> 00:19:14.625
Thank you so much.

180
00:19:15.541 --> 00:19:17.333
I'll pay you back as soon as I can.

181
00:19:18.333 --> 00:19:19.541
Don't worry about that.

182
00:19:23.750 --> 00:19:24.583
Take this.

183
00:19:33.041 --> 00:19:35.291
May the Buddha protect
a good man like you.

184
00:19:38.583 --> 00:19:39.458
Thank you. ma'am.

185
00:19:50.875 --> 00:19:51.708
Sir.

186
00:19:52.541 --> 00:19:53.791
This is for the debt.

187
00:19:58.000 --> 00:19:58.833
You keep it.

188
00:20:05.875 --> 00:20:06.875
[sighs]

189
00:20:11.583 --> 00:20:12.791
Then the debt's cleared.

190
00:20:14.458 --> 00:20:15.583
Go tell your grandma.

191
00:20:17.000 --> 00:20:18.708
-Okay?
-Does that hurt?

192
00:20:30.458 --> 00:20:32.250
Is that an angel's wing?

193
00:20:35.333 --> 00:20:36.666
[sighs softly]

194
00:20:39.625 --> 00:20:41.500
Thank you for helping me and Grandma.

195
00:20:46.375 --> 00:20:48.166
I paid off all your debt. Grandma.

196
00:20:58.708 --> 00:21:00.333
[gasping]

197
00:21:00.958 --> 00:21:03.041
[retching. coughing]

198
00:21:06.333 --> 00:21:07.708
[gags. strains]

199
00:21:09.458 --> 00:21:10.916
[breath trembling]

200
00:21:20.458 --> 00:21:22.291
[coughs]

201
00:21:33.333 --> 00:21:34.541
[prisoner] Oh. shit.

202
00:21:34.625 --> 00:21:37.291
Sir. sir! Someone's down! Sir!

203
00:21:38.458 --> 00:21:39.500
[gasps]

204
00:21:39.583 --> 00:21:40.583
[chain rattling]

205
00:21:40.666 --> 00:21:42.250
[doctor] You have a brain tumor.

206
00:21:44.166 --> 00:21:48.000
That's what's causing the seizures.
the vomiting and the blackouts.

207
00:21:48.541 --> 00:21:52.333
You could hear things too.
or see things that aren't there.

208
00:21:53.291 --> 00:21:56.791
In your case. the tumor is inoperable.

209
00:21:57.708 --> 00:21:58.833
It's too dangerous.

210
00:21:59.958 --> 00:22:02.791
I recommend radiotherapy
to manage the symptoms.

211
00:22:08.666 --> 00:22:09.750
How long do I have?

212
00:22:10.750 --> 00:22:12.458
Mm. with radiotherapy.

213
00:22:13.291 --> 00:22:15.041
you may have up to a year.

214
00:22:16.333 --> 00:22:18.708
Without it. you might have…

215
00:22:19.708 --> 00:22:20.583
less than a month.

216
00:22:26.416 --> 00:22:28.000
[horn honks in distance]

217
00:22:32.791 --> 00:22:33.666
[exhales]

218
00:22:37.541 --> 00:22:39.541
-[inhales deeply]
-[water trickling]

219
00:22:40.666 --> 00:22:41.666
[spits]

220
00:22:41.750 --> 00:22:42.583
[gulps]

221
00:22:42.666 --> 00:22:44.250
[gargling]

222
00:22:47.125 --> 00:22:47.958
[spits]

223
00:22:48.458 --> 00:22:50.958
[panting softly]

224
00:23:07.583 --> 00:23:08.583
[sniffles]

225
00:23:08.666 --> 00:23:10.666
-[clattering]
-[Grandma Lek sobbing]

226
00:23:12.500 --> 00:23:14.541
-[Nid Noi crying]
-[Grandma Lek yelps]

227
00:23:21.375 --> 00:23:24.208
Please don't do this. I'm begging you.

228
00:23:24.291 --> 00:23:27.666
-I'm begging you.
-For what. huh? What is it?

229
00:23:27.750 --> 00:23:29.375
-Huh? This?
-[screams]

230
00:23:29.958 --> 00:23:31.708
You can't even come up with one payment.

231
00:23:31.791 --> 00:23:33.708
-Grandma!
-[sobbing]

232
00:23:39.708 --> 00:23:41.000
Hey! Little shit!

233
00:23:41.083 --> 00:23:42.541
[Grandma Lek and Nid Noi screaming]

234
00:23:42.625 --> 00:23:43.458
[thug 1] Hey!

235
00:23:46.000 --> 00:23:47.083
[thug 2 grunts]

236
00:23:48.833 --> 00:23:50.291
[panting]

237
00:23:54.541 --> 00:23:55.625
[thug 3] You piece of shit.

238
00:23:59.125 --> 00:24:01.375
-[Grandma Lek and Nid Noi scream]
-[thug 3 grunts]

239
00:24:01.458 --> 00:24:02.750
[thug 3 groans]

240
00:24:09.625 --> 00:24:11.583
-Fuck you!
-[Grandma Lek and Nid Noi scream]

241
00:24:13.833 --> 00:24:14.875
[thug 3] Oh!

242
00:24:15.833 --> 00:24:17.958
-This motherfucker.
-You're dead. yeah?

243
00:24:18.791 --> 00:24:19.708
Let's do it.

244
00:24:20.708 --> 00:24:23.333
-[motorcycle engine whirring]
-The cops are here.

245
00:24:24.000 --> 00:24:25.375
Bro. what do we do?

246
00:24:25.458 --> 00:24:26.500
-Get out.
-Let's go!

247
00:24:29.750 --> 00:24:31.083
[sniffles. exhales]

248
00:24:40.583 --> 00:24:41.500
What's all this?

249
00:24:42.083 --> 00:24:45.708
Sir. the debt collector gang
broke up the lady's stall.

250
00:24:45.791 --> 00:24:47.708
and that man stepped in to help her.

251
00:24:50.125 --> 00:24:52.125
Is that right? You want to press charges?

252
00:24:52.750 --> 00:24:55.958
I… I can… actually file a charge?

253
00:24:56.041 --> 00:25:00.375
Yeah. Just go to the station
and tell the duty officer to log it.

254
00:25:02.916 --> 00:25:05.166
Hey. you. Go with her as a witness.

255
00:25:13.250 --> 00:25:16.583
I'm sure you know. ma'am.
these black market loans are illegal.

256
00:25:17.125 --> 00:25:18.875
This is what happens when you can't pay.

257
00:25:21.750 --> 00:25:22.583
All right.

258
00:25:23.291 --> 00:25:24.208
How can we help?

259
00:25:25.458 --> 00:25:27.000
Do you know how many there were?

260
00:25:27.500 --> 00:25:29.250
Can you describe the culprits?

261
00:25:30.083 --> 00:25:32.625
Each time. there are always four.

262
00:25:32.708 --> 00:25:36.500
Hey. kid. Black shirt. Remove your hat.

263
00:25:40.375 --> 00:25:42.583
Hey. Go on.

264
00:25:45.083 --> 00:25:46.625
Remove your fucking hat.

265
00:25:52.166 --> 00:25:53.458
Ah. it's Num.

266
00:25:54.958 --> 00:25:56.291
When did they let you out?

267
00:25:57.416 --> 00:25:59.208
-What shit are you up to now?
-Khem.

268
00:26:00.416 --> 00:26:01.625
This guy protected her.

269
00:26:02.625 --> 00:26:05.375
He jumped in to help when
the debt collector gang attacked her.

270
00:26:06.458 --> 00:26:07.583
Am I hearing that right?

271
00:26:08.833 --> 00:26:09.666
Lady.

272
00:26:10.458 --> 00:26:11.458
Do you know who he is?

273
00:26:12.083 --> 00:26:13.708
He's a ruthless debt collector.

274
00:26:15.083 --> 00:26:17.625
He killed a debtor
and spent ten years in prison.

275
00:26:19.708 --> 00:26:21.041
What lies you been telling her?

276
00:26:22.333 --> 00:26:25.458
Mr. Num didn't lie to us.
He helped me and Grandma.

277
00:26:32.791 --> 00:26:34.333
Get Num's details as well.

278
00:26:37.541 --> 00:26:39.125
-[footsteps departing]
-[door opens]

279
00:26:40.041 --> 00:26:40.916
[door closes]

280
00:26:47.291 --> 00:26:48.583
We'll make our way back.

281
00:26:55.041 --> 00:26:56.750
I won't trouble you anymore. Num.

282
00:26:59.291 --> 00:27:00.500
I can give you a ride.

283
00:27:02.416 --> 00:27:03.625
You got a lot to carry.

284
00:27:06.416 --> 00:27:09.416
It'll be fine. You can just
leave everything right here.

285
00:27:12.500 --> 00:27:13.333
I…

286
00:27:15.291 --> 00:27:17.041
