-[gasps]

298
00:28:07.708 --> 00:28:10.500
Huh? Huh? Why are you calling her?

299
00:28:11.000 --> 00:28:13.708
Why are you calling her?
Huh? Can you tell me why?

300
00:28:17.000 --> 00:28:18.041
No. [gasps]

301
00:28:20.708 --> 00:28:22.666
When I say how much you'll pay.

302
00:28:22.750 --> 00:28:23.833
you pay.

303
00:28:24.583 --> 00:28:26.750
