309
00:28:59.375 --> 00:29:01.375
[suspenseful music playing]

310
00:29:14.875 --> 00:29:16.458
[Grandma Lek gasping]

311
00:29:21.958 --> 00:29:23.041
Nid Noi. come here.

312
00:29:24.416 --> 00:29:26.416
[Nid Noi whimpering]

313
00:29:26.500 --> 00:29:28.208
-[thug] Old bitch! Open up!
-[both scream]

314
00:29:29.375 --> 00:29:31.250
-I said. open up. damn it!
-[shutters rattling]

315
00:29:33.250 --> 00:29:34.500
Where's that motherfucker?

316
00:29:34.583 --> 00:29:35.875
[breath trembling]

317
00:29:38.791 --> 00:29:40.875
Lady. come out and talk.

318
00:29:42.666 --> 00:29:44.333
Open up and we'll discuss this.

319
00:29:46.916 --> 00:29:48.250
[sighs]

320
00:29:50.916 --> 00:29:51.958
You owe us…

321
00:29:53.541 --> 00:29:54.791
and you called the cops.

322
00:29:56.333 --> 00:29:58.125
But we own them. Know that.

323
00:29:59.958 --> 00:30:02.541
[cries] I didn't know.

324
00:30:03.833 --> 00:30:06.083
A cop said I should do it. [sniffling]

325
00:30:08.583 --> 00:30:09.416
{\an8}Come out.

326
00:30:11.458 --> 00:30:12.291
{\an8}Come out.

327
00:30:13.541 --> 00:30:15.166
-Come out. I said!
-[rattles loudly]

328
00:30:15.250 --> 00:30:17.583
-You old bitch! Didn't you hear me?
-[wailing]

329
00:30:17.666 --> 00:30:20.708
-Stupid cow! Come out! Come out!
-[screams]

330
00:30:21.250 --> 00:30:23.250
