-[Grandma Lek whimpering]

331
00:30:26.125 --> 00:30:28.041
[objects clattering]

332
00:30:32.875 --> 00:30:34.375
So are you going to come out?

333
00:30:38.708 --> 00:30:40.791
[gasping]

334
00:30:45.666 --> 00:30:47.041
{\an8}Then both die in there.

335
00:30:48.416 --> 00:30:49.375
Crazy bitch!

336
00:30:50.458 --> 00:30:51.833
[both scream]

337
00:30:51.916 --> 00:30:53.666
[gasping]

338
00:30:57.500 --> 00:30:59.041
[Nid Noi sobbing]

339
00:30:59.125 --> 00:31:01.041
[sobbing]

340
00:31:02.333 --> 00:31:04.208
[yells]

341
00:31:07.083 --> 00:31:09.000
[both sobbing]

342
00:31:11.875 --> 00:31:12.916
[gasps. screams]

343
00:31:17.333 --> 00:31:19.791
[sobbing] I'm begging you.

344
00:31:21.833 --> 00:31:22.791
I give up.

345
00:31:29.958 --> 00:31:30.833
Okay.

346
00:31:32.458 --> 00:31:33.666
Get the tape.

347
00:31:36.666 --> 00:31:38.916
Fuck sake! Go get the tape. man.

348
00:31:40.333 --> 00:31:41.750
[gasping]

349
00:31:42.333 --> 00:31:43.208
[Po] Tape her hands.

350
00:31:44.916 --> 00:31:46.541
-[tape rips]
-No!

351
00:31:47.916 --> 00:31:49.833
[wailing]

352
00:31:54.541 --> 00:31:56.875
-[explosion]
-[screams]

353
00:31:59.208 --> 00:32:00.666
-Grandma!
-Nid Noi!

354
00:32:03.291 --> 00:32:05.500
[wailing. sobbing]

355
00:32:06.791 --> 00:32:07.625
Nid Noi!

356
00:32:08.291 --> 00:32:09.458
Help! Nid Noi!

357
00:32:11.708 --> 00:32:13.041
Help! Help!

358
00:32:14.041 --> 00:32:15.375
Help me. help!

359
00:32:17.291 --> 00:32:18.333
Nid Noi!

360
00:32:19.083 --> 00:32:20.708
Help! Help me!

361
00:32:25.458 --> 00:32:28.208
GAS

362
