365
00:33:18.000 --> 00:33:20.375
<i>Her hands were stuck</i>
<i>to the shutters in prayer.</i>

366
00:33:24.750 --> 00:33:27.583
-[flames whooshing]
-[Grandma Lek and Nid Noi screaming]

367
00:33:29.916 --> 00:33:31.041
