<i>they saw Po's car there.</i>

369
00:33:39.541 --> 00:33:40.916
<i>And his gang running away.</i>

370
00:33:41.541 --> 00:33:42.750
<i>They did it. all right.</i>

371
00:33:44.208 --> 00:33:46.250
<i>But let's face it. they're untouchable.</i>

372
00:33:49.083 --> 00:33:51.125
<i>Oh. the granddaughter.</i>

373
00:33:51.208 --> 00:33:52.291
