for the next of kin. just in case?

381
00:34:24.375 --> 00:34:25.208
Sir?

382
00:34:29.208 --> 00:34:30.250
[sighs]

383
00:34:30.333 --> 00:34:32.083
[low pensive music playing]

384
00:34:59.541 --> 00:35:01.208
What have you come to pray for. Num?

385
00:35:09.500 --> 00:35:11.458
For a little girl I know to get better.

386
00:35:13.125 --> 00:35:14.666
My disciple called me.

387
00:35:16.666 --> 00:35:18.750
