-Ugh! I'm paying.

397
00:36:04.375 --> 00:36:06.458
-I'm definitely paying today.
-Oh. really?

398
00:36:07.666 --> 00:36:09.958
-Next time. watch yourself.
-Don't do that.

399
00:36:10.750 --> 00:36:12.708
