-[thug 1] Oh. this food's good.

400
00:36:15.750 --> 00:36:17.958
-Hey. cheers. Cheers.
-[glasses clink]

401
00:36:24.333 --> 00:36:25.625
[thug 2] Holy fuck.

402
00:36:27.875 --> 00:36:29.958
This glue is really good shit.

403
00:36:32.041 --> 00:36:32.958
From now on.

404
00:36:34.208 --> 00:36:36.250
any debtor who doesn't pay.

405
00:36:36.333 --> 00:36:39.875
I'm gonna pour this
down their nose and mouth.

406
00:36:39.958 --> 00:36:41.958
[all laughing]

407
00:36:42.958 --> 00:36:44.250
Hey. cheers to that.

408
00:36:44.916 --> 00:36:46.250
-Cheers. Yeah.
-[all] Cheers.

409
00:36:46.750 --> 00:36:48.750
-[siren wailing]
-[suspenseful music playing]

410
00:36:51.833 --> 00:36:52.833
[siren chirping]

411
00:36:54.916 --> 00:36:56.666
-[laughs]
-You can't help yourself.

412
00:36:58.708 --> 00:37:00.458
-What? You again?
-Hey!

413
00:37:00.541 --> 00:37:02.958
-[grunts]
-Hey. hey. hey. What the fuck?

414
00:37:03.041 --> 00:37:04.125
[people clamoring]

415
00:37:07.208 --> 00:37:08.166
Piece of shit!

416
00:37:08.750 --> 00:37:12.208
[yelling in pain]

417
00:37:12.833 --> 00:37:14.041
[groaning]

418
00:37:18.166 --> 00:37:19.000
Shit.

419
00:37:37.041 --> 00:37:39.250
Piece of shit! [groaning]

420
00:37:50.250 --> 00:37:51.500
You dirty motherfucker!

421
00:37:52.416 --> 00:37:54.083
[thug grunting]

422
00:37:54.708 --> 00:37:56.500
-[knife slashing]
-[thug grunting]

423
00:38:17.208 --> 00:38:18.541
[groaning]

424
00:38:22.625 --> 00:38:23.625
[gags]

425
00:38:24.750 --> 00:38:26.708
[gasping]

426
00:38:30.916 --> 00:38:32.041
{\an8}Where's Po hiding?

427
00:38:33.125 --> 00:38:34.541
[gasping]

428
00:38:49.416 --> 00:38:52.416
[breath trembling. whimpering]

429
00:38:55.708 --> 00:38:58.708
[screaming]

430
00:39:04.083 --> 00:39:05.583
Do I have to ask you again?

431
00:39:05.666 --> 00:39:07.625
-[whimpering]
-Where's Po?

432
00:39:16.500 --> 00:39:19.166
-[thug screams]
-[lively chatter]

433
00:39:30.791 --> 00:39:31.958
[dealer] Let's see the cards.

434
00:39:34.375 --> 00:39:35.500
Player. nine points.

435
00:39:37.833 --> 00:39:39.083
Player. natural eight.

436
00:39:53.833 --> 00:39:56.500
GOLD PAWN

437
00:39:56.583 --> 00:39:57.708
Let me borrow 10.000.

438
00:40:04.916 --> 00:40:05.750
Jod.

439
00:40:11.291 --> 00:40:12.500
