471
00:43:00.458 --> 00:43:02.458
[both grunting]

472
00:43:20.875 --> 00:43:22.875
[Num breathing heavily]

473
00:43:36.708 --> 00:43:39.750
-[explosion]
-[gunshots]

474
00:43:41.625 --> 00:43:43.416
[screaming]

475
00:43:45.500 --> 00:43:50.625
[screaming in pain]

476
00:44:05.333 --> 00:44:06.791
[tires screech]

477
00:44:06.875 --> 00:44:08.875
[people clamoring]

478
00:44:15.625 --> 00:44:17.750
[thug] Hey. stop! Come back! Stop!

479
00:44:24.166 --> 00:44:26.166
[panting]

480
00:44:27.625 --> 00:44:28.458
[water splashes]

481
00:44:29.916 --> 00:44:31.541
Hey. stop! Stop!

482
00:44:32.208 --> 00:44:33.041
I'm a cop.

483
00:44:34.250 --> 00:44:35.125
Hands in the air.

484
00:44:37.791 --> 00:44:38.791
Hands in the air!

485
00:44:41.708 --> 00:44:42.833
Do you hear me?

486
00:44:52.708 --> 00:44:53.833
What the fuck's this?

487
00:44:53.916 --> 00:44:55.625
Guys. stay back. Stay back. Hey!

488
00:44:55.708 --> 00:44:57.208
No! Oh! [yelps]

489
00:44:59.166 --> 00:45:01.083
[gasps]

490
00:45:01.166 --> 00:45:02.250
[sighs] No!

491
00:45:10.708 --> 00:45:13.000
-[crackling]
-[winces. thuds]

492
00:45:17.458 --> 00:45:19.458
[suspenseful music playing]

493
00:45:33.208 --> 00:45:36.583
{\an8}SAENGTAWAN CHILDREN'S HOME FOUNDATION

494
00:45:55.125 --> 00:45:57.916
Hey! What the fuck
are you doing. you prick?

495
00:46:01.000 --> 00:46:03.375
You bastard. why the fuck
are you sniffing around?

496
00:46:03.458 --> 00:46:05.625
-Motherfucker!
-[Ong] Stop meddling. you fuck.

497
00:46:05.708 --> 00:46:07.000
What's your fucking problem?

498
00:46:07.083 --> 00:46:08.375
-You think you're tough?
-Stop!

499
00:46:10.333 --> 00:46:11.166
[grunts]

500
00:46:16.166 --> 00:46:18.083
[grunting]

501
00:46:26.833 --> 00:46:28.458
[thudding]

502
00:46:33.833 --> 00:46:37.875
Num! That's enough!
He's going to die! [panting]

503
00:46:44.958 --> 00:46:46.000
[Mr. Tom] What happened?

504
00:46:46.083 --> 00:46:49.583
EAT IT ALL. DON'T WASTE A MORSEL
FOOD IS PRECIOUS

505
00:46:49.666 --> 00:46:52.833
Ong was messing with Phueng.
Num and I stopped them.

506
00:46:55.500 --> 00:46:56.958
[Mr. Tom] Is that true. Phueng?

507
00:47:00.916 --> 00:47:02.333
Don't stare her down!

508
00:47:02.416 --> 00:47:03.916
You did it. Now own it.

509
00:47:04.000 --> 00:47:04.875
-[grunts]
-[groans]

510
00:47:06.000 --> 00:47:07.083
[groans]

511
00:47:07.166 --> 00:47:08.625
I wasn't asking you.

512
00:47:09.541 --> 00:47:10.500
Stay out of it.

513
00:47:12.333 --> 00:47:14.250
You're nothing but a troublemaker.

514
00:47:15.791 --> 00:47:16.916
You little shit!

515
00:47:18.958 --> 00:47:21.083
Your parents are shit as well.

516
00:47:23.583 --> 00:47:28.083
Good for nothing but fucking and breeding.
and then they can't afford to raise you!

517
00:47:29.750 --> 00:47:31.708
For fuck's sake. you little shits.

518
00:47:32.333 --> 00:47:33.625
You're the dregs of society.

519
00:47:35.708 --> 00:47:37.500
-[Young Num grunts]
-Hmm?

520
00:47:39.000 --> 00:47:39.875
Hmm?

521
00:47:40.583 --> 00:47:41.750
[growls] Asshole!

522
00:47:42.333 --> 00:47:44.583
-[grunts]
-[clattering]

523
00:47:50.125 --> 00:47:52.125
[panting]

524
00:48:14.041 --> 00:48:15.791
[Young Kong] Mr. Tom called the police.

525
00:48:18.875 --> 00:48:19.708
[Young Num] Fuck it.

526
00:48:21.541 --> 00:48:23.375
